1
00:00:58,170 --> 00:01:00,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whew, I'm full!</font>

2
00:01:01,580 --> 00:01:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Demon Defense Force again?</font>

3
00:01:04,330 --> 00:01:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I just consumed Mira,
so I don't have room for seconds.</font>

4
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Mune ga shizunde mirai kanjirenaku nattari</font>

5
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Toki ga tomatte mou owatta tte kanjitari</font>

6
00:01:35,630 --> 00:01:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Fusagikonde hanasenakute</font>

7
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Jiwari kokoro no kasa ga hiraita</font>

8
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Soredemo tsuyogatte ikiteta</font>

9
00:01:45,830 --> 00:01:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Nagusamete nante iwanai</font>

10
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Tsuyoku natte mae o mitetainda</font>

11
00:01:54,790 --> 00:02:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Dakedo yowasa ga oshitsubusu</font>

12
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kimi ni atte sekai afurete hikari ataetekuretari</font>

13
00:02:07,630 --> 00:02:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Sukoshi datte kibou nakatta boku ga waraetetanda</font>

14
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Nanigenai kaiwa de zutto egao ataetekuretari</font>

15
00:02:17,290 --> 00:02:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Arigatou tte terete warau kara iwanai yo</font>

16
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Dakedo omotteru yo</font>

17
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kono saki mae muite ikeru kana?</font>

18
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Hikari yo, boku ni</font>

19
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:46,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="60">Yokohama Showdown</font>

20
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:46,000
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Episode 10</b></font>

21
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whew, I'm full!</font>

22
00:03:04,210 --> 00:03:06,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Demon Defense Force again?</font>

23
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I just consumed Mira,
so I don't have room for seconds.</font>

24
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gorgeous power.</font>

25
00:03:32,380 --> 00:03:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mira's skills certainly are
fitting of a commander!</font>

26
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How dare you!</font>

27
00:03:40,130 --> 00:03:41,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now then...</font>

28
00:03:41,290 --> 00:03:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let me hear it!</font>

29
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Praise the glorious Kuusetsu!</font>

30
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wild Mountain Cherry Blossoms!</font>

31
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm telling you...</font>

32
00:04:08,460 --> 00:04:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">that won't work!</font>

33
00:04:11,170 --> 00:04:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She managed to stop
my lightning-fast slash attack?!</font>

34
00:04:23,630 --> 00:04:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You thought that was enough
to fight a god?</font>

35
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just so you know,</font>

36
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">at their full power, the rest of the
Eight Thunder Gods are stronger than I am.</font>

37
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, I'm going to
surpass them eventually.</font>

38
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The only reason you're still alive
is 'cause Big Sis Shikoku thought ahead.</font>

39
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You. You're Yuuki Wakura, yes?</font>

40
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Turning down my lovely invitation earlier?</font>

41
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You've got some nerve.</font>

42
00:05:00,580 --> 00:05:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's pick up where we left off
in our current forms.</font>

43
00:05:05,330 --> 00:05:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are you kidding me?!</font>

44
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm going to make you mine.</font>

45
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Any woman who gets near my brother...</font>

46
00:05:33,330 --> 00:05:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">won't live to tell the tale!</font>

47
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Big Sis!</font>

48
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A new challenger?</font>

49
00:05:49,330 --> 00:05:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can feel Coco and Naon's energies.</font>

50
00:05:56,130 --> 00:05:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're inside of her!</font>

51
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The people she assimilated
are still alive?</font>

52
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then that means-</font>

53
00:06:05,290 --> 00:06:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll force her to purge Mira
and the others!</font>

54
00:06:07,210 --> 00:06:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Right!</font>

55
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is where we put Kuusetsu down!</font>

56
00:06:12,330 --> 00:06:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Can you still say that once you see this?</font>

57
00:06:24,210 --> 00:06:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I consumed Mira.</font>

58
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So I can use her ability now.</font>

59
00:06:44,130 --> 00:06:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shall I destroy the city
and put a new god on the map?</font>

60
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Time for the ace up my sleeve!</font>

61
00:06:56,130 --> 00:06:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Follow the person in front of you
and keep moving!</font>

62
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sector Three to HQ.</font>

63
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We're nearly finished
evacuating the residents.</font>

64
00:07:06,290 --> 00:07:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What is that thing?!</font>

65
00:07:14,130 --> 00:07:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that a... Shuuki?!</font>

66
00:07:18,330 --> 00:07:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Holy... It's enormous!</font>

67
00:07:24,460 --> 00:07:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I didn't know they could get that big!</font>

68
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't let it intimidate you, Yuuki!</font>

69
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Looks like Mira made a miscalculation
keeping me here!</font>

70
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mira made the right decision.</font>

71
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If we let you escape,
it'll be too risky to deal with you later.</font>

72
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:45,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So instead,</font>

73
00:07:45,210 --> 00:07:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">she gets consumed and
we throw a clone party?</font>

74
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We are the Demon Defense Force!</font>

75
00:07:54,170 --> 00:07:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The real battle begins now!</font>

76
00:07:59,380 --> 00:08:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lady Ren!</font>

77
00:08:01,670 --> 00:08:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We're ready to send reinforcements
to Yokohama!</font>

78
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Our finest combat specialists!</font>

79
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now allow me to reiterate!</font>

80
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kuusetsu! This is where you die!</font>

81
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm going to trample you
with my godly army!</font>

82
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am the Supreme Commander
of the Demon Defense Force!</font>

83
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Give it your best shot, I dare ya!</font>

84
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Supreme Commander...</font>

85
00:08:53,290 --> 00:08:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Supreme Commander?
So she's the top dog?</font>

86
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That makes her worth beating!</font>

87
00:08:58,790 --> 00:09:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey, wait!</font>

88
00:09:01,420 --> 00:09:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They took the bait.</font>

89
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll draw them over to the bridge.</font>

90
00:09:04,830 --> 00:09:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Keep us ahead of them.</font>

91
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aw, jeez. What a bunch of sheep.</font>

92
00:09:10,830 --> 00:09:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There are less of them now!</font>

93
00:09:12,380 --> 00:09:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We owe Miss Tovera big time!</font>

94
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Should we get in there, too?</font>

95
00:09:25,540 --> 00:09:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Good. All the cars are cleared out, too.</font>

96
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Take us down.</font>

97
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay.</font>

98
00:09:35,170 --> 00:09:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's a lot of 'em.</font>

99
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Buy me some time.</font>

100
00:09:39,380 --> 00:09:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You got it.</font>

101
00:09:43,830 --> 00:09:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here goes!</font>

102
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bam, bam, bam, bam, bam, bam!</font>

103
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Great One!</font>

104
00:10:05,580 --> 00:10:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Feather bullets...</font>

105
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're no joke.</font>

106
00:10:09,290 --> 00:10:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Battering my hands to pieces in seconds...</font>

107
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fine, then!</font>

108
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll just keep summoning new hands!
They'll serve as our tank!</font>

109
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How long will you last?
Can't wait to find out!</font>

110
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's enough divine punishment, I think.</font>

111
00:11:04,130 --> 00:11:06,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow, you're a stubborn one!</font>

112
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But you're already exhausted.</font>

113
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:12,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's finish it off with ten more seconds!</font>

114
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:15,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How about a visit
from a hail of godly gunfire?!</font>

115
00:11:16,130 --> 00:11:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All in favor?</font>

116
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aye!</font>

117
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Stand down, Maia.</font>

118
00:11:26,130 --> 00:11:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm ready to soak it up.</font>

119
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ephemeral!</font>

120
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What did... you do?</font>

121
00:11:56,540 --> 00:11:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I stole your life force.</font>

122
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:09,210
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Azuma Years</b></font>

123
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:09,210
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Ephemeral</b></font>

124
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:09,210
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Direct Contact</b></font>

125
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ephemeral: Direct Contact!</font>

126
00:12:18,250 --> 00:12:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Excellent work, Lady Tovera.</font>

127
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nice job standin' your ground, Maia.</font>

128
00:12:28,540 --> 00:12:31,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Feels like my senses
are in their prime again!</font>

129
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lady Ren!</font>

130
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">According to the report we received,</font>

131
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">they succeeded
at dividing the enemy's forces.</font>

132
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">However, Yokohama's still in trouble...</font>

133
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes, I'm aware.</font>

134
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll use my ability to join the fight
from Washington.</font>

135
00:13:10,580 --> 00:13:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ren's ability:</font>

136
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All-Encompassing Lord of the Cosmos.</font>

137
00:13:19,330 --> 00:13:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She boosts her power by reflecting
the same ability in both of her eyes.</font>

138
00:14:27,540 --> 00:14:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What you did just now...
Did you aim it at Japan?</font>

139
00:14:32,630 --> 00:14:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It won't hit any aircraft,
so there's no need to worry.</font>

140
00:14:37,380 --> 00:14:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Using an ability that powerful,
and she didn't even break a sweat.</font>

141
00:14:43,380 --> 00:14:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My subordinates will handle the rest.</font>

142
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's continue our meeting.</font>

143
00:14:48,290 --> 00:14:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ren Yamashiro...</font>

144
00:14:50,380 --> 00:14:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She truly is Earth's answer.</font>

145
00:14:55,880 --> 00:14:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The emergency exit is this way!</font>

146
00:14:58,290 --> 00:15:01,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Protecting the injured
should be prioritized above all else!</font>

147
00:15:23,170 --> 00:15:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, look!</font>

148
00:15:25,210 --> 00:15:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shouldn't you be a little more concerned
about that thing?</font>

149
00:15:30,580 --> 00:15:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's got a pretty brutal ability.</font>

150
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Y'see-</font>

151
00:15:49,130 --> 00:15:50,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

152
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Supreme Commander.</font>

153
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She sent cover fire from America.</font>

154
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It was too big.</font>

155
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">An easy target.</font>

156
00:16:05,460 --> 00:16:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That was my ace in the hole...</font>

157
00:16:09,830 --> 00:16:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That was the ace in the hole
that Big Sis Shikoku gave me!</font>

158
00:16:16,460 --> 00:16:17,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki!</font>

159
00:16:17,330 --> 00:16:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">On it!</font>

160
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ame-no-Mitori.</font>

161
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's got range!</font>

162
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nice work!</font>

163
00:16:41,170 --> 00:16:42,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Miss Tenka!</font>

164
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">During battle, the briefest words
can hold the most meaning.</font>

165
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And Yuuki's feelings hit the mark!</font>

166
00:17:06,210 --> 00:17:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My clones are slow and clumsy.</font>

167
00:17:08,630 --> 00:17:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Perhaps it takes practice to master.</font>

168
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That said, my real body...</font>

169
00:17:16,210 --> 00:17:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">isn't so harmless!</font>

170
00:17:22,130 --> 00:17:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What are you doing... to my sister?!</font>

171
00:17:28,330 --> 00:17:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Where did that power come from?!</font>

172
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This one was a clone, too!</font>

173
00:17:40,130 --> 00:17:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm right over here!</font>

174
00:17:45,630 --> 00:17:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Looks like phasing works better in combat
than my slime ability.</font>

175
00:17:52,710 --> 00:17:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What are you doing...</font>

176
00:17:55,210 --> 00:17:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">TO MY BROTHER?!</font>

177
00:18:05,710 --> 00:18:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now you get...</font>

178
00:18:08,670 --> 00:18:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">all my power...</font>

179
00:18:12,130 --> 00:18:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">in one shot!</font>

180
00:18:48,330 --> 00:18:49,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I got her?!</font>

181
00:18:57,670 --> 00:19:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're as strong as a commander, too.</font>

182
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She's started setting traps
by hiding her clones in the ground.</font>

183
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll take care of your backup
after I finish you off.</font>

184
00:19:46,330 --> 00:19:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">'Cause I can keep on fighting forever.</font>

185
00:19:55,420 --> 00:19:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki...</font>

186
00:19:58,040 --> 00:19:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Activate your Heavenward form.</font>

187
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I think that's our only option!</font>

188
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Be sure and make the most of it!</font>

189
00:20:08,130 --> 00:20:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes, ma'am!</font>

190
00:20:12,500 --> 00:20:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I get to see your trump card now?</font>

191
00:20:16,250 --> 00:20:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki?</font>

192
00:20:18,080 --> 00:20:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki...</font>

193
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="78">HEAVENWARD</font>

194
00:20:41,630 --> 00:20:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Heavenward!</font>

195
00:20:44,460 --> 00:20:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Miss Mira... I'm on my way to save you!</font>

196
00:20:56,880 --> 00:21:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Love beam!</font>

197
00:21:11,330 --> 00:21:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Shiritai teka shitai furetai</font>

198
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Afuredasu kono omoi wa tomannai janai</font>

199
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Amai amai sono karada de uketomete ne darling</font>

200
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kainarashite ageru gohoubi no jikan</font>

201
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kasaneawasu hada to hada kara umareru netsu de</font>

202
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Juuden max</font>

203
00:21:38,750 --> 00:21:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Ima hassha OK!</font>

204
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kono te kara ima love love beam</font>

205
00:21:44,130 --> 00:21:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Sono heart megake ima love love beam</font>

206
00:21:47,830 --> 00:21:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kokoro no kyori mo tobikoeteku</font>

207
00:21:51,670 --> 00:21:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Zero kyori de hanate</font>

208
00:21:53,830 --> 00:21:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay!</font>

209
00:21:55,330 --> 00:21:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Nigasanai wa mou love love beam</font>

210
00:21:58,750 --> 00:22:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Sekai no hate mademo love love beam</font>

211
00:22:02,380 --> 00:22:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Sou ai koso ga sekai o kaeru</font>

212
00:22:06,130 --> 00:22:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kurayami mo somero heart iro ni</font>

213
00:22:26,290 --> 00:22:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A tremendous torrent of power.</font>

214
00:22:30,420 --> 00:22:35,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Seems Yuuki Wakura
also has a lot of potential.</font>

215
00:22:35,210 --> 00:22:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I like that.</font>

216
00:22:39,670 --> 00:22:41,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If Himari drags her feet,</font>

217
00:22:41,670 --> 00:22:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then perhaps I'll send in the others
to help lock him down.</font>

218
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hmm...</font>

219
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">First, I can take the lead
and teach 'em the basics...</font>

220
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">More enemies on the way!</font>

221
00:23:17,250 --> 00:23:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh good!</font>

222
00:23:20,420 --> 00:23:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's do this!</font>

223
00:23:21,670 --> 00:23:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We're in the homestretch!</font>

224
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="69">Slave: Heaven</font>

225
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:30,130
<font size="40"><b>Episode 11</b></font>

226
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Next time!</font>

227
00:23:27,630 --> 00:23:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Episode 11, "Slave: Heaven"</font>

228
00:23:30,420 --> 00:23:31,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">For today's bonus...</font>

229
00:23:32,040 --> 00:23:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your present. Is. Me!</font>

230
00:23:35,670 --> 00:23:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've always wanted to try this!</font>

231
00:23:37,540 --> 00:23:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I hope you'll accept
the chocolates... and me!</font>

